---
description: Shopify app concerns for Vercel hosting and app lifecycle events
alwaysApply: true
---

# Shopify and Deployment Constraints

- Assume deployment target is Vercel.
- Build app behavior to work as a proper Shopify app behind the required proxy setup.
- Keep Shopify-specific integration logic isolated from core domain services.

# Lifecycle and Webhooks

- Ensure webhook registration and app setup tasks are handled as part of deployment/runtime bootstrap flows.
- Make webhook handlers idempotent and safe to retry.
- Keep webhook processing logic in services, not in thin HTTP handlers.

# Operational Safety

- Prefer explicit logging and error handling for external Shopify calls.
- Keep integration boundaries clear so future non-Shopify features can evolve independently.
